<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Profile Incompletion Notice - Blue Sky</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222021;">

    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f4f7f9; padding: 30px 0;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                    style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">

                    <!-- Header with Logo -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" bgcolor="#055a90" style="padding: 20px;">
                            <img src="<%= app_url %>Logo.png" alt="Blue Sky Logo"
                                style="display: block; max-height: 50px;" />
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 30px 40px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;">
                            <p><strong>Hello <%= user_name %>,</strong></p>

                            <p>Weâ€™ve reviewed your profile and noticed that some information is incomplete. To proceed with your profile approval, please review your profile details carefully.</p>

                            <!-- Notice Box -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="15" cellspacing="0"
                                style="background-color: #eef6fb; border-left: 4px solid #055a90; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="font-size: 15px; color: #222021;">
                                        <strong>Message:</strong><br />
                                        <%= message %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <p>If you need any assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

                            <!-- Optional button - you can add a link here -->
                            <!-- <p>
                                <a href="<%= app_url %>profile-review" 
                                   style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #055a90; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
                                   Review Your Profile
                                </a>
                            </p> -->

                            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br /><strong>Blue Sky Admin Team</strong></p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" bgcolor="#055a90" style="color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
                            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Blue Sky. All rights reserved.
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>

</html>
